Title: Globalization and location choice: an analysis of US multinational firms in 1980 and 2000
Pages: 1187-1210
Author-Name: Ricardo G Flores
Author-Workplace-Name: Department of Business Administration, College of Business, University of Illinois at Champaign-Urbana, IL, USA
Author-Name: Ruth V Aguilera
Author-Workplace-Name: Department of Business Administration, College of Business, University of Illinois at Champaign-Urbana, IL, USA
