Title: International new ventures: revisiting the influences behind the &lsquo;born-global&rsquo; firm
Pages: 1113-1131
Author-Name: Terence Fan
Author-Workplace-Name: Lee Kong Chian School of Business, Singapore Management University, Singapore, Singapore
Author-Name: Phillip Phan
Author-Workplace-Name: Lally School of Management &amp; Technology, Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute, Troy, USA
